sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant vLLM as vLLM/SGLang Engine<br/>5557/TCP ZMQ PUB
    participant ZMQ as zmqSubscriber<br/>ZMQ SUB
    participant Pool as kvevents.Pool<br/>Sharded Workers
    participant Adapter as EngineAdapter<br/>(vLLM/SGLang)
    participant Index as kvblock.Index<br/>(LRU/Ristretto/Redis)
    participant EPP as llm-d EPP<br/>(Host Process)
    participant Indexer as kvcache.Indexer
    participant TP as TokenProcessor<br/>FNV-64a/CBOR
    participant UDS as uds_tokenizer<br/>UDS gRPC
    participant HF as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over vLLM,Index: Flow 1: KV-Event Ingestion (Write Path)
        vLLM->>ZMQ: BlockStored / BlockRemoved / AllBlocksCleared<br/>ZMQ PUB/SUB 5557/TCP (msgpack)
        ZMQ->>Pool: Raw event dispatch<br/>FNV-1a shard by pod ID
        Pool->>Adapter: Parse engine-specific event
        Adapter->>Index: Add / Evict / Clear blocks<br/>engineKey to requestKey mapping
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over EPP,TP: Flow 2: Pod Scoring (Read Path)
        EPP->>Indexer: ScoreTokens(tokens, podSet)<br/>In-process Go API
        Indexer->>TP: Compute block keys<br/>FNV-64a over CBOR tokens
        TP-->>Indexer: Block key sequence
        Indexer->>Index: Lookup(blockKeys, podSet)
        Index-->>Indexer: Per-pod hit counts
        Indexer-->>EPP: Scored pod rankings<br/>(sub-millisecond latency)
    end

    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
        Note over EPP,HF: Flow 3: Tokenization (Sidecar)
        EPP->>UDS: RenderChatCompletion(request)<br/>gRPC over UDS (no encryption)
        Note over UDS: First request for model
        UDS->>HF: Download tokenizer files<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP, TLS 1.2+, Bearer Token
        HF-->>UDS: Tokenizer model artifacts
        UDS-->>EPP: Token IDs + multimodal features<br/>gRPC response over UDS
    end

    rect rgb(255, 230, 255)
        Note over vLLM,HF: Flow 4: KV-Cache Offloading
        Note over vLLM: llmd_fs_backend plugin<br/>(in-process)
        vLLM->>vLLM: GPU to CPU staging<br/>CUDA memcpy (async batch)
        vLLM->>vLLM: CPU to Shared Storage<br/>POSIX I/O or S3 HTTPS/443
        vLLM-->>ZMQ: ZMQ PUB event (optional)<br/>Block offloaded notification
    end
